          <h2>Our Mission</h2>
          <p>It is our purpose to spread the gospel of Jesus Christ and the love of God. We seek to be a church that demonstrates the power and the love of God to the best of our ability through serving and making disciples of God’s people and equipping them to do the same.
            <br><a href="{{ sitevars.urlpath }}about/our-mission.html">learn more</a>
